code: @Override protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     EndpointType type = getCamelContext().getTypeConverter().mandatoryConvertTo(EndpointType.class, remaining).     return new SparkEndpoint(uri, this, type). }
